column5: How is the lake level on LOW? Are there any issues motoring through Welcome Way or Holmstrom's Marsh areas?
The graph at lwcb.ca shows that the level is down about 18 inches from a normal July reservoir level.
Holmstroms show 3 feet minimum on sonar if you stay in the middle. It's mud bottom so no big deal anyway. Welcome channel is plenty deep as always.
